                'content'           => "<p><span style=\\\"font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\\\"></span><span style=\\\"font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\\\">1、进入首页头部搜索区域查找商品。</span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\\\"><br/></span></p><p><img src=\\\"http://test.b2b2c.ecjia.com/content/uploads/data/descimg/20150915/14422815902464.png\\\" title=\\\"14422815902464.png\\\" alt=\\\"sqq1.png\\\"/></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\\\"font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\\\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\\\">2、进入商品详情界面，点击立即购买或者加入购物车即可</span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\\\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\\\"></span></p><p><img src=\\\"http://test.b2b2c.ecjia.com/content/uploads/data/descimg/20150915/14422816773959.png\\\" title=\\\"14422816773959.png\\\" alt=\\\"QQ截图20150915094747.png\\\"/></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\\\"font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\\\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\\\">3、若是加入购物，则可以点击右下角的购物车图标进入购物车界面</span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\\\"><br/></span></p><p><img src=\\\"http://test.b2b2c.ecjia.com/content/uploads/data/descimg/20150915/14422818413010.png\\\" title=\\\"14422818413010.png\\\" alt=\\\"QQ截图20150915095029.png\\\"/></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\\\"font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\\\"></span><span style=\\\"font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\\\">4、去结算，点击提交订单</span></p><p><br/></p><p><img src=\\\"http://test.b2b2c.ecjia.com/content/uploads/data/descimg/20150915/14422819194090.png\\\" title=\\\"14422819194090.png\\\" alt=\\\"QQ截图20150915095145.png\\\"/></p><p><br/><br/> &nbsp;<span style=\\\"font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\\\"></span><span style=\\\"font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\\\">5、查看订单状态</span></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\\\"font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\\\"></span></p><p><img src=\\\"http://test.b2b2c.ecjia.com/content/uploads/data/descimg/20150915/14422819872365.png\\\" title=\\\"14422819872365.png\\\" alt=\\\"QQ截图20150915095258.png\\\"/></p><p><br/></p>",
