                'content'           => "<p><span style=\\\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 18px;\\\">例如：我需要购买康佳LED</span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 18px;\\\">可以通过&quot;筛选分类&quot;和&quot;直接搜索&quot;来查找相应的商品</span><span style=\\\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 14px;\\\"></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 14px;\\\"><br/></span></p><p><strong><span style=\\\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 16px;\\\">一、筛选分类</span></strong></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 16px;\\\">1、点击底部“列表”按钮进入商品分类列表界面</span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 16px;\\\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 16px;\\\"></span></p><p><img src=\\\"http://test.b2b2c.ecjia.com/content/uploads/data/descimg/20150915/14422852444777.png\\\" title=\\\"14422852444777.png\\\" alt=\\\"sqq11.png\\\"/></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 14px;\\\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 16px;\\\">2、找到您所要购买商品的所属分类点击进入查看即可</span><span style=\\\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 16px;\\\"></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 16px;\\\"><br/></span></p><p><img src=\\\"http://test.b2b2c.ecjia.com/content/uploads/data/descimg/20150915/14422852976592.png\\\" title=\\\"14422852976592.png\\\" alt=\\\"22.png\\\"/></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p><br/><span style=\\\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 16px;\\\"></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 16px;\\\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 16px;\\\"></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 16px;\\\">二、直接搜索商品</span><span style=\\\"font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\\\"><br/><span style=\\\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 16px;\\\">1、<span style=\\\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\\\">进入首页头部搜索区域查找商品。</span></span><span style=\\\"font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\\\"></span></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\\\"><br/></span></span></p><p><img src=\\\"http://test.b2b2c.ecjia.com/content/uploads/data/descimg/20150915/14422815902464.png\\\" title=\\\"14422815902464.png\\\" alt=\\\"sqq1.png\\\"/></p>",
