                'content'           => "<p style=\\\"padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 21px; font-family: Arial, Verdana, 宋体; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\"><span style=\\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 16px;\\\">订单拆分有以下几种情况：</span></p><p style=\\\"padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 21px; font-family: Arial, Verdana, 宋体; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\"><span style=\\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 16px;\\\">1.您所购买的商品库房分布不同；</span></p><p style=\\\"padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 21px; font-family: Arial, Verdana, 宋体; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\"><span style=\\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 16px;\\\">2.您所购买的商品发货方不同（<span style=\\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 16px;\\\">由<span style=\\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\\\">第三方卖家或由ECJia发货）</span></span>；</span></p><p style=\\\"padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 21px; font-family: Arial, Verdana, 宋体; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\"><span style=\\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 16px;\\\">3.您选择了有货先发；</span></p><p style=\\\"padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 21px; font-family: Arial, Verdana, 宋体; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\"><span style=\\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 16px;\\\">如以上几种情况您都不属于，您可以联系客服为您解答。</span></p><p><br/></p>",
